A wakeup alarm written in PyObjc. User creates a 'playables' and 'wakeups' composed of playables.
Extremely configurable with hooks for play,stop, snooze. Works with iTunes and Mplayer.
Quite involved yet on the whole simple.

User should be somewhat familiar with Python.

For some reason one has to install 
See http://www.stat.purdue.edu/~sguha/wakeupalarm.html for more details.
